{"name": "arcadia-sdk", "metadata": {"name": "arcadia-sdk", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["black", "build", "click", "logtail-python", "loguru", "pre-commit", "pytest", "python-dotenv", "rich", "supabase", "twine"], "summary": "arcadia is a platform for ml developers to host and get paid for their proprietary ml models.", "upload_time": 1734854894}, "documentation": ["# Arcadia SDK\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <!-- You could add a logo image here -->\n  <h3 align=\"center\">Deploy and Monetize ML Models with Ease</h3>\n</p>\n\nArcadia is a powerful platform that enables machine learning developers to seamlessly deploy, manage, and monetize their models. With our SDK, you can transform your ML models into production-ready APIs in minutes.\n\n## \u2728 Features\n\n- \ud83d\ude80 **One-Click Deployment**: Deploy models to production with a single command\n- \ud83d\udcb0 **Built-in Monetization**: Set pricing and start earning from your models instantly\n- \ud83d\udcca **Advanced Monitoring**: Track performance, usage metrics, and revenue in real-time\n- \ud83d\udd12 **Enterprise-Grade Security**: SOC 2 compliant with end-to-end encryption\n- \ud83d\udd04 **Version Control**: Manage multiple versions of your models effortlessly\n- \ud83d\udcc8 **Auto-scaling**: Handle varying loads with automatic scaling\n\n## \ud83d\ude80 Quick Start\n\n### Installation\n\n```bash\npip install arcadia-sdk\n```\n\n### Usage\n\n```python\nfrom arcadia import Model, predict\n\n@predict\ndef my_model(input_data):\n    # Your model logic here\n    return prediction\n\nModel(\"my-model\").deploy()\n```\n\n### Documentation\n\nFor more detailed documentation, please refer to the [Arcadia Documentation](https://docs.arcadia.dev).\n\n### Support\n\nFor support, please refer to the [Arcadia Support](https://support.arcadia.dev).\n\n### License\n\nThis project is licensed under the MIT License - see the [LICENSE](LICENSE) file for details.\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "arcadia.modules", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "arcadia.modules.login.cli", "xref": {"fqname": "arcadia.modules.login.cli.cli", "project": null}}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.load_credentials", "xref": {"fqname": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.load_credentials", "project": null}}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.save_credentials", "xref": {"fqname": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.save_credentials", "project": null}}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.validate_credentials", "xref": {"fqname": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.validate_credentials", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.auth", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.save_credentials", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "username", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "api_key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Save credentials to config file"]}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.load_credentials", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Load credentials from config file"]}, {"name": "arcadia.modules.login.auth.validate_credentials", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "username", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "api_key", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name":